{
  "text": "I'm just interested in the problem here that we sometimes have with transmission since the word others was used three times in the transmission rather than the word self. And could you give me an idea of the problem in communication that we have there that creates that type of an anomaly, which if I didn't catch could create a rather large discrepancy in communication. Firstly, we may note the clumsiness of language and our unfamiliarity with it in our a native, shall we say, experience? Secondly, we may point out that once we have miscalled or misnumbered an event or a thing that referent is quite likely to be reused for some a transmission, a time, as you call this enmeasurement, a due to our original error having gone undetected by ourselves.",
